01:24:13,979 --> 01:24:14,340
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, dobro,

1538
01:24:14,340 --> 01:24:15,359
[SPEAKER_00] i vi ste mangup, znate,

1539
01:24:15,359 --> 01:24:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda od kogore.

1540
01:24:16,000 --> 01:24:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, dobro, nisam ja takav.

1541
01:24:16,920 --> 01:24:18,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ja druga,

1542
01:24:18,260 --> 01:24:19,659
[SPEAKER_01] ne zna se boriti sa njima,

1543
01:24:19,659 --> 01:24:20,300
[SPEAKER_01] sa znanjem.

1544
01:24:20,300 --> 01:24:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] I ova, što sam ti još reći.

1545
01:24:21,920 --> 01:24:24,220
[SPEAKER_01] I naslovnice jutarnjega lista,

1546
01:24:24,220 --> 01:24:25,180
[SPEAKER_01] moja slika, ono,

1547
01:24:25,500 --> 01:24:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] zblzine,

1548
01:24:26,420 --> 01:24:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] dobro, onda sam bio mlađahan,

1549
01:24:28,300 --> 01:24:29,699
[SPEAKER_01] nisam ni sad star,

1550
01:24:29,699 --> 01:24:30,500
[SPEAKER_01] baš se nadam,

1551
01:24:30,500 --> 01:24:31,739
[SPEAKER_01] iako imam godina,

1552
01:24:31,739 --> 01:24:32,899
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

1553
01:24:32,899 --> 01:24:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] ali baš u duhu nisam

1554
01:24:35,279 --> 01:24:36,100
[SPEAKER_01] ostario.

1555
01:24:36,100 --> 01:24:37,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ova, što je dobro.

1556
01:24:37,739 --> 01:24:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] I ovaj, kako se zove?

1557
01:24:38,960 --> 01:24:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] I piše tamo,

1558
01:24:40,539 --> 01:24:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] admiral Davod,

1559
01:24:41,659 --> 01:24:43,039
[SPEAKER_01] da vam je rekao da će rat,

1560
01:24:43,039 --> 01:24:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] početi u Rijeci.

1561
01:24:44,380 --> 01:24:46,020
[SPEAKER_01] Rat, početi,

1562
01:24:46,020 --> 01:24:47,180
[SPEAKER_01] svjetski rat početi

1563
01:24:47,180 --> 01:24:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] 2025. godine u Rijeci.

1564
01:24:50,000 --> 01:24:53,199
[SPEAKER_01] Čak ni u tom tekstu,

1565
01:24:53,199 --> 01:24:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] nema nigdje da se nam to rekao,

1566
01:24:54,779 --> 01:24:55,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali bitan naslov,

1567
01:24:55,619 --> 01:24:56,800
[SPEAKER_01] ko čita teksta unutra.

1568
01:24:56,800 --> 01:24:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] Naslovi palaju.

1569
01:24:57,619 --> 01:24:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] I sad to ti ono znaš,

1570
01:24:59,119 --> 01:24:59,460
[SPEAKER_01] evo ga,

1571
01:24:59,460 --> 01:25:00,819
[SPEAKER_01] poludio,

1572
01:25:00,819 --> 01:25:01,359
[SPEAKER_01] admiral,

1573
01:25:01,359 --> 01:25:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] u mirovini sad,

1574
01:25:02,300 --> 01:25:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne zna šta će,

1575
01:25:03,039 --> 01:25:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] pa šta pričate.

1576
01:25:03,920 --> 01:25:05,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nigdje to nisam rekao.

1577
01:25:05,380 --> 01:25:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ali u čemu je,

1578
01:25:06,760 --> 01:25:08,239
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam napisao tamo,

1579
01:25:08,239 --> 01:25:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] što je sve potvrdilo točno ovo,

1580
01:25:09,800 --> 01:25:11,060
[SPEAKER_01] 24, 25 sad,

1581
01:25:11,060 --> 01:25:12,699
[SPEAKER_01] znači 25 će biti krešenja.

1582
01:25:12,699 --> 01:25:14,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači živimo u posljednjim vremenima.

1583
01:25:14,340 --> 01:25:15,399
[SPEAKER_00] Je, je,

1584
01:25:15,399 --> 01:25:16,500
[SPEAKER_01] u posljednjim vremenima,

1585
01:25:16,500 --> 01:25:17,399
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno Mergedona,

1586
01:25:17,399 --> 01:25:18,439
[SPEAKER_01] zato sam napisao knjigu

1587
01:25:18,439 --> 01:25:19,399
[SPEAKER_01] u vremenama Mergedona,

1588
01:25:19,399 --> 01:25:20,859
[SPEAKER_01] u vrući mir tri.

1589
01:25:20,859 --> 01:25:22,579
[SPEAKER_01] I ovaj, šta se ti rekao?

1590
01:25:22,579 --> 01:25:23,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam teba rekao,

1591
01:25:23,560 --> 01:25:25,340
[SPEAKER_01] da će se svi događaj,

1592
01:25:25,340 --> 01:25:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] geopolitički,

1593
01:25:26,300 --> 01:25:28,279
[SPEAKER_01] kada će vrkuna s toga biti

1594
01:25:28,279 --> 01:25:29,180
[SPEAKER_01] u 25. godine,

1595
01:25:29,699 --> 01:25:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] odvijati na prvim vratima Euroazije,

1596
01:25:32,199 --> 01:25:33,560
[SPEAKER_01] velikim dijelom

1597
01:25:33,560 --> 01:25:34,899
[SPEAKER_01] i manjim dijelom

1598
01:25:34,899 --> 01:25:36,439
[SPEAKER_01] na drugim vratima Euroazije.

1599
01:25:36,439 --> 01:25:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] I sad definiram ta prva vrjeta Euroazije,

1600
01:25:39,260 --> 01:25:40,319
[SPEAKER_01] kažem,

1601
01:25:40,319 --> 01:25:42,060
[SPEAKER_01] to su od rijeke,

1602
01:25:42,060 --> 01:25:43,159
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, od Istrije,

1603
01:25:43,159 --> 01:25:44,720
[SPEAKER_01] od rijeke sam uzeo kao rijeku,

1604
01:25:44,720 --> 01:25:46,319
[SPEAKER_01] sinonim grada najvećega,

1605
01:25:46,319 --> 01:25:47,899
[SPEAKER_01] i sve do Izraela.

1606
01:25:47,899 --> 01:25:49,619
[SPEAKER_01] I u dubini Ukrajina.

1607
01:25:49,619 --> 01:25:51,399
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Ukrajina ja tada govorim tada.

1608
01:25:51,399 --> 01:25:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] Je li se to dogodilo?

1609
01:25:53,960 --> 01:25:54,199
[SPEAKER_01] Je.

1610
01:25:54,199 --> 01:25:55,920
[SPEAKER_01] E, ali,

1611
01:25:55,920 --> 01:25:57,260
[SPEAKER_01] sada,

1612
01:25:57,260 --> 01:25:58,899
[SPEAKER_01] kad ti staviš 25. godine,

1613
01:25:59,020 --> 01:25:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] admiral je rekao,

1614
01:25:59,619 --> 01:26:00,779
[SPEAKER_01] pošće je treći svjetski rat,

1615
01:26:00,779 --> 01:26:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] ja to nigdje nisam rekao,

1616
01:26:01,960 --> 01:26:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije bitno.

1617
01:26:03,039 --> 01:26:05,380
[SPEAKER_01] Res, meni je to služilo dobro,

1618
01:26:05,380 --> 01:26:07,699
[SPEAKER_01] da knjiga se izuzetno čitala.

1619
01:26:07,699 --> 01:26:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro prodavala, da.

1620
01:26:08,739 --> 01:26:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro prodavala, to je jedna,

1621
01:26:10,340 --> 01:26:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] nego je što je došla kod ljudi,

1622
01:26:11,739 --> 01:26:12,100
[SPEAKER_01] a znači,

1623
01:26:12,100 --> 01:26:13,060
[SPEAKER_01] sve ono došlo vrijeme,

1624
01:26:13,060 --> 01:26:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] evo sad je ljeto bila,

1625
01:26:14,119 --> 01:26:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] uzet ću knjigu,

1626
01:26:14,840 --> 01:26:16,140
[SPEAKER_01] pa ću čitati ljeto.

1627
01:26:16,140 --> 01:26:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] Danas mi ljudi zaustavljaju.

1628
01:26:16,840 --> 01:26:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] Čitaću lošu, je li?

1629
01:26:17,800 --> 01:26:19,079
[SPEAKER_01] E, čitaću lošu, tako bi.

1630
01:26:19,079 --> 01:26:20,680
[SPEAKER_01] i sad me ljudi zaustavljaju,

1631
01:26:20,680 --> 01:26:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] sad ovih dana,

1632
01:26:22,079 --> 01:26:23,520
[SPEAKER_01] jer je to toliko aktualno,

1633
01:26:23,520 --> 01:26:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] i mi kožu,

1634
01:26:24,380 --> 01:26:24,720
[SPEAKER_01] admiral,

1635
01:26:24,720 --> 01:26:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] pa kako ste vi mogli to,

1636
01:26:26,800 --> 01:26:30,479
[SPEAKER_01] još te 2025. u svojom knjizi gospodari,

1637
01:26:30,479 --> 01:26:31,479
[SPEAKER_01] kao se napisati,

1638
01:26:31,479 --> 01:26:32,720
[SPEAKER_01] a to se sve sada događa.

1639
01:26:32,720 --> 01:26:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ću ja onako pravo pitati,

1640
01:26:35,300 --> 01:26:35,859
[SPEAKER_00] admiral,

1641
01:26:35,859 --> 01:26:37,979
[SPEAKER_00] ali što onda nas čeka?

1642
01:26:37,979 --> 01:26:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] Još ove godine,

1643
01:26:39,039 --> 01:26:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] 2025.

1644
01:26:39,579 --> 01:26:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] Što nas čeka?

1645
01:26:40,619 --> 01:26:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo mi malo strateški razmišljati

1646
01:26:43,039 --> 01:26:44,220
[SPEAKER_00] u sljedećih 10-20 godina.

1647
01:26:44,220 --> 01:26:45,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako, što nas čeka?

1648
01:26:45,319 --> 01:26:48,359
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo, Hrvatska treba,

1649
01:26:48,359 --> 01:26:50,060
[SPEAKER_01] kad je ovo manje od mjesec dana,

1650
01:26:50,060 --> 01:26:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] treba riješiti svoj untarnji,

1651
01:26:52,960 --> 01:26:54,199
[SPEAKER_01] determinirani kaos

1652
01:26:54,199 --> 01:26:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] koje je sama proizvela.

1653
01:26:55,420 --> 01:26:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je auntention.

1654
01:26:56,960 --> 01:26:58,439
[SPEAKER_01] Nama ne treba neko iz vani,

1655
01:26:58,439 --> 01:26:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] dovoljno smo mi i sami,

1656
01:26:59,619 --> 01:27:00,859
[SPEAKER_01] ne treba na niko duš vani,

1657
01:27:00,859 --> 01:27:01,619
[SPEAKER_01] ništa nam ne treba.

1658
01:27:02,020 --> 01:27:03,520
[SPEAKER_01] Još ako se neki duš vani pojavi,

1659
01:27:03,520 --> 01:27:04,600
[SPEAKER_01] još da možemo ujediniti,

1660
01:27:04,600 --> 01:27:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] kao što smo u domovinskom ratu.

1661
01:27:05,960 --> 01:27:08,159
[SPEAKER_01] Već zanimljivo je da je

1662
01:27:08,159 --> 01:27:09,520
[SPEAKER_01] predsjednik Pilanović govorio

1663
01:27:09,520 --> 01:27:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] o vladi nacionalnog jedinstva,

1664
01:27:11,199 --> 01:27:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] je li tako?

1665
01:27:11,699 --> 01:27:14,359
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno mu je bila usporedba

1666
01:27:14,359 --> 01:27:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] sa tim,

1667
01:27:14,760 --> 01:27:16,460
[SPEAKER_01] 1991. godina kada je bila vlada

1668
01:27:16,460 --> 01:27:17,439
[SPEAKER_01] nacionalnog jedinstva,

1669
01:27:17,439 --> 01:27:18,399
[SPEAKER_01] kada je Tušman.

1670
01:27:18,399 --> 01:27:20,720
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, očigledno je državo pogibjeli,

1671
01:27:20,720 --> 01:27:23,479
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije toliko izvansko na agresiju,

1672
01:27:23,479 --> 01:27:24,640
[SPEAKER_01] nego unutarnju.

1673
01:27:24,640 --> 01:27:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] Nima unutarnju agresiju.

1674
01:27:26,500 --> 01:27:28,800
[SPEAKER_01] To što je ovo u strategiji definirava.

1675
01:27:29,199 --> 01:27:30,520
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, unutarnja agresija

1676
01:27:30,520 --> 01:27:32,859
[SPEAKER_01] kada su sve institucije blokirane.

1677
01:27:32,859 --> 01:27:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] Danas su sve institucije blokirane.

1678
01:27:34,699 --> 01:27:35,680
[SPEAKER_01] U Hrvatskoj.

1679
01:27:35,680 --> 01:27:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ne funkcionira.

1680
01:27:36,380 --> 01:27:38,939
[SPEAKER_01] Od Sabora do ovoga,

1681
01:27:38,939 --> 01:27:39,640
[SPEAKER_01] kako se zove,

1682
01:27:39,640 --> 01:27:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ustavnog suda,

1683
01:27:41,079 --> 01:27:43,119
[SPEAKER_01] sada ne bram sve drugo što je ostaloga.

1684
01:27:43,119 --> 01:27:45,520
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ako je to unutarnja agresija,

1685
01:27:45,520 --> 01:27:46,819
[SPEAKER_01] ona se samo unutarnjom snagom

1686
01:27:46,819 --> 01:27:48,500
[SPEAKER_01] može i prezriješiti.

1687
01:27:48,500 --> 01:27:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] Niko vam ne može izvani.

1688
01:27:50,039 --> 01:27:51,199
[SPEAKER_01] da je u hemahina,

1689
01:27:51,199 --> 01:27:51,760
[SPEAKER_01] kao što je bilo

1690
01:27:51,760 --> 01:27:52,859
[SPEAKER_01] u grčkim strategijama,

1691
01:27:52,859 --> 01:27:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatskom slučaju

1692
01:27:53,840 --> 01:27:54,579
[SPEAKER_01] ono ne vrijedi.

1693
01:27:54,579 --> 01:27:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedno.

1694
01:27:55,960 --> 01:27:56,840
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo,

1695
01:27:56,840 --> 01:27:58,979
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da će najviše utjecati

1696
01:27:58,979 --> 01:28:00,180
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj geopolitički,

1697
01:28:00,180 --> 01:28:02,479
[SPEAKER_01] globalni strateški poremećaj

1698
01:28:02,479 --> 01:28:04,640
[SPEAKER_01] i da ne našo zaslugo,

1699
01:28:04,640 --> 01:28:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] mi ćemo se,

1700
01:28:05,420 --> 01:28:07,340
[SPEAKER_01] moglo bi i našom zaslugo,

1701
01:28:07,340 --> 01:28:09,060
[SPEAKER_01] onda bi tada bilo ozbiljni grači,

1702
01:28:09,060 --> 01:28:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] to sam već rekao,

1703
01:28:09,859 --> 01:28:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] biti na pravoj strani povijesti.

1704
01:28:13,640 --> 01:28:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sve će ovisiti

1705
01:28:15,119 --> 01:28:16,300
[SPEAKER_01] od ovih izbora

1706
01:28:16,300 --> 01:28:19,279
[SPEAKER_01] za kad je 17. travnja.

1707
01:28:19,279 --> 01:28:20,560
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, od njih

1708
01:28:20,560 --> 01:28:21,380
[SPEAKER_01] ko će biti?

1709
01:28:21,380 --> 01:28:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] Hoće li ova briselska ekipa

1710
01:28:27,039 --> 01:28:27,979
[SPEAKER_01] ostati dalje,

1711
01:28:27,979 --> 01:28:29,859
[SPEAKER_01] pa uništao još malo što je ostalo?

1712
01:28:29,859 --> 01:28:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ili će doći neka nova ekipa?

1713
01:28:32,420 --> 01:28:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, SDP nije taj

1714
01:28:35,380 --> 01:28:36,859
[SPEAKER_01] koji bi on mogao promijeniti,

1715
01:28:36,859 --> 01:28:38,020
[SPEAKER_01] jer on po svom habitusu

1716
01:28:38,020 --> 01:28:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] ne može promijeniti

1717
01:28:38,960 --> 01:28:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] ova nova vremena.

1718
01:28:39,960 --> 01:28:41,020
[SPEAKER_01] A jesu li oprostite

1719
01:28:41,020 --> 01:28:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] što vas prekidame?

1720
01:28:41,800 --> 01:28:43,399
[SPEAKER_00] Milanović i Plenković

1721
01:28:43,399 --> 01:28:44,520
[SPEAKER_00] dva lica istog

1722
01:28:44,520 --> 01:28:45,899
[SPEAKER_00] globalističkog novčića.

1723
01:28:45,899 --> 01:28:47,159
[SPEAKER_01] Resimo, to ima

1724
01:28:47,159 --> 01:28:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] takve postavke.

1725
01:28:47,920 --> 01:28:49,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, slušaj,

1726
01:28:49,119 --> 01:28:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] ako ovo što bi ja sada rekao

1727
01:28:50,539 --> 01:28:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] da bi se opredijelio

1728
01:28:51,239 --> 01:28:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] za jednu stranu

1729
01:28:51,800 --> 01:28:52,359
[SPEAKER_01] u ovoj emisiji,

1730
01:28:52,359 --> 01:28:53,399
[SPEAKER_01] ja se ne želim opredijeliti

1731
01:28:53,399 --> 01:28:54,840
[SPEAKER_01] na jednu stranu,

1732
01:28:54,840 --> 01:28:56,899
[SPEAKER_01] a da ovo što govorim

1733
01:28:56,899 --> 01:28:58,399
[SPEAKER_01] da dobro gledatelji odvagnu

1734
01:28:58,399 --> 01:28:59,579
[SPEAKER_01] i da oni pronađu

1735
01:28:59,579 --> 01:29:00,720
[SPEAKER_01] tu pravu stranu.

1736
01:29:00,720 --> 01:29:02,079
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tako ću odgovoriti.

1737
01:29:02,079 --> 01:29:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne želim

1738
01:29:02,960 --> 01:29:03,739
[SPEAKER_01] i neću.

1739
01:29:03,739 --> 01:29:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] Kao strategiju

1740
01:29:04,880 --> 01:29:05,520
[SPEAKER_01] bilo bi to

1741
01:29:05,520 --> 01:29:06,319
[SPEAKER_01] popuno pogrešno.

1742
01:29:06,319 --> 01:29:06,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ko što sam ja

1743
01:29:06,920 --> 01:29:08,119
[SPEAKER_01] nisem opredijelio

1744
01:29:08,119 --> 01:29:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] u ovoj ukrajinskoj

1745
01:29:10,079 --> 01:29:10,680
[SPEAKER_01] za rusku

1746
01:29:10,680 --> 01:29:12,319
[SPEAKER_01] ili za bilo koju drugu stranu.

1747
01:29:12,319 --> 01:29:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] To što ja govorim

1748
01:29:13,699 --> 01:29:14,500
[SPEAKER_01] istinu što će biti,

1749
01:29:14,500 --> 01:29:15,439
[SPEAKER_01] a to se je potvrdilo,

1750
01:29:15,439 --> 01:29:16,739
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj da je.

1751
01:29:16,739 --> 01:29:17,319
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, tako neću

1752
01:29:17,319 --> 01:29:18,020
[SPEAKER_01] ni u ovom slučaju.

1753
01:29:19,000 --> 01:29:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] ali da će ići

1754
01:29:20,199 --> 01:29:21,300
[SPEAKER_01] u brzase procesi

1755
01:29:21,300 --> 01:29:22,340
[SPEAKER_01] to sigurno znam.

1756
01:29:22,340 --> 01:29:26,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ako pobjedi jedna strana,

1757
01:29:26,600 --> 01:29:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] neimenujući drugo,

1758
01:29:27,659 --> 01:29:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] tada je moguće

1759
01:29:30,260 --> 01:29:31,159
[SPEAKER_01] da se nastavi

1760
01:29:31,159 --> 01:29:32,159
[SPEAKER_01] ova agonija

1761
01:29:32,159 --> 01:29:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] i izgubit ćemo

1762
01:29:34,920 --> 01:29:35,840
[SPEAKER_01] podosta vremena.

1763
01:29:35,840 --> 01:29:38,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znam ja da mene

1764
01:29:38,119 --> 01:29:38,819
[SPEAKER_01] mnogi pitaju,

1765
01:29:38,819 --> 01:29:39,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa dobro,

1766
01:29:39,300 --> 01:29:41,159
[SPEAKER_01] ovi su bili,

1767
01:29:41,159 --> 01:29:42,260
[SPEAKER_01] misli se ovo,

1768
01:29:42,260 --> 01:29:43,079
[SPEAKER_01] komunizam,

1769
01:29:43,079 --> 01:29:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek komunizam.

1770
01:29:43,800 --> 01:29:44,699
[SPEAKER_01] Komunizam je davno,

1771
01:29:44,699 --> 01:29:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] ima gore ideologije

1772
01:29:45,739 --> 01:29:46,220
[SPEAKER_01] od komunizma.

1773
01:29:46,220 --> 01:29:46,600
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao sam,

1774
01:29:46,600 --> 01:29:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je militantni liberalizam,

1775
01:29:48,060 --> 01:29:49,899
[SPEAKER_01] svi smo zarobljenici

1776
01:29:49,899 --> 01:29:53,359
[SPEAKER_01] te antikristove ideologije.

1777
01:29:53,359 --> 01:29:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ono je bila antikristova,

1778
01:29:54,699 --> 01:29:56,560
[SPEAKER_01] a ovo je antikristova

1779
01:29:56,560 --> 01:29:57,520
[SPEAKER_01] na treću potenciju.

1780
01:29:57,520 --> 01:30:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ideologije živimo,

1781
01:30:00,119 --> 01:30:01,319
[SPEAKER_01] ispranih mozgova,

1782
01:30:01,319 --> 01:30:02,199
[SPEAKER_01] više ili manje.

1783
01:30:02,199 --> 01:30:03,720
[SPEAKER_01] Tada će se,

1784
01:30:03,720 --> 01:30:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] opet uvijek govorimo

1785
01:30:04,779 --> 01:30:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] o jakos trajcijene.

1786
01:30:05,739 --> 01:30:07,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ako pobjedi ona,

1787
01:30:07,600 --> 01:30:08,140
[SPEAKER_01] što ja mislim

1788
01:30:08,140 --> 01:30:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] da bi trebalo pobjedi,

1789
01:30:09,199 --> 01:30:11,439
[SPEAKER_01] i ako se sastavi vlada

1790
01:30:11,439 --> 01:30:13,199
[SPEAKER_01] koja bi bila na tragu

1791
01:30:13,199 --> 01:30:14,939
[SPEAKER_01] te vlade

1792
01:30:14,939 --> 01:30:16,060
[SPEAKER_01] nacionalnog jedinstva,

1793
01:30:16,060 --> 01:30:17,899
[SPEAKER_01] a vladu nacionalnog jedinstva,

1794
01:30:18,720 --> 01:30:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] ako žele uistiti dobro Hrvatsko,

1795
01:30:20,000 --> 01:30:21,720
[SPEAKER_01] može sastaviti jedna ili druga strana

1796
01:30:21,720 --> 01:30:22,479
[SPEAKER_01] ko dobije vlaste.

1797
01:30:22,479 --> 01:30:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] To je ključeno.

1798
01:30:24,859 --> 01:30:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači treba pronaći snage

1799
01:30:27,000 --> 01:30:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] koje će okrenuti,

1800
01:30:28,239 --> 01:30:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] poznati umne ljude u Hrvatsko

1801
01:30:30,239 --> 01:30:31,180
[SPEAKER_01] ovako i reći,

1802
01:30:31,180 --> 01:30:31,399
[SPEAKER_01] ajde,

1803
01:30:31,399 --> 01:30:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] zato u svakdje postoji

1804
01:30:32,800 --> 01:30:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] vijeće mudraca,

1805
01:30:33,619 --> 01:30:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] vijeće svijedi i glava,

1806
01:30:34,739 --> 01:30:37,079
[SPEAKER_01] a to znači preko 75 godine,

1807
01:30:37,079 --> 01:30:38,899
[SPEAKER_01] kada tada mudrost dolazi.

1808
01:30:38,899 --> 01:30:39,640
[SPEAKER_01] Mudrost ne možeš,

1809
01:30:39,640 --> 01:30:40,319
[SPEAKER_01] možeš imati znanje,

1810
01:30:40,319 --> 01:30:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne znaš da imaš mudru.

1811
01:30:41,779 --> 01:30:43,279
[SPEAKER_01] Sa 20 ili 30, da.

1812
01:30:43,520 --> 01:30:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] Mogu okrenuti Hrvatsko

1813
01:30:45,039 --> 01:30:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] i onda sjesti i raspravljati

1814
01:30:46,659 --> 01:30:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] ko što mi raspravljamo

1815
01:30:47,840 --> 01:30:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] u ovom ovdje emisiji vašog.

1816
01:30:51,239 --> 01:30:52,859
[SPEAKER_01] Sve smo stavili na sto,

1817
01:30:52,859 --> 01:30:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] evo.

1818
01:30:53,260 --> 01:30:55,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, pitam li odgovaratel.

1819
01:30:55,600 --> 01:30:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] Tako i drugi.

1820
01:30:56,920 --> 01:30:58,939
[SPEAKER_01] Još je bolje kada bi sučeljavali se.

1821
01:30:58,939 --> 01:30:59,359
[SPEAKER_01] Još bolje.

1822
01:30:59,359 --> 01:31:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Onda se izvirsili mnoge stvari.

1823
01:31:00,699 --> 01:31:02,859
[SPEAKER_01] I to će biti za Hrvatsko.

1824
01:31:02,859 --> 01:31:04,859
[SPEAKER_01] A ako to ne bude tako,

1825
01:31:04,859 --> 01:31:07,560
[SPEAKER_01] onda uistinu se možemo

1826
01:31:07,560 --> 01:31:10,300
[SPEAKER_01] zabrinuti za našu domovnu

1827
01:31:10,300 --> 01:31:10,979
[SPEAKER_01] i naš narod,

1828
01:31:10,979 --> 01:31:12,359
[SPEAKER_01] kojega je nažalost sve manje,

1829
01:31:12,359 --> 01:31:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] koji je udaljio se

1830
01:31:14,680 --> 01:31:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] od svojih hršćanskih katoliških korijena,

1831
01:31:16,920 --> 01:31:20,859
[SPEAKER_01] u kojim je crkva prilati,

1832
01:31:20,859 --> 01:31:23,140
[SPEAKER_01] crkveni, izgubljeni u prostoru i vremenu.

1833
01:31:23,140 --> 01:31:26,020
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost u Vatikanu je instaliran

1834
01:31:26,020 --> 01:31:29,920
[SPEAKER_01] čovjek koji je njihov igrač

1835
01:31:29,920 --> 01:31:31,819
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj okultne oligarhije.

1836
01:31:31,819 --> 01:31:33,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mu neću reći funkciju,

1837
01:31:33,359 --> 01:31:34,260
[SPEAKER_01] ne ime, najmanje.

1838
01:31:34,260 --> 01:31:37,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj papa zvan Buanosera,

1839
01:31:37,560 --> 01:31:40,060
[SPEAKER_01] zamislite vi da on kada je dobio pontifikat,

1840
01:31:40,060 --> 01:31:41,859
[SPEAKER_01] pojavi se ispred

1841
01:31:41,859 --> 01:31:45,939
[SPEAKER_01] puk hršćanskog katoliškog svjetoga Petra

1842
01:31:45,939 --> 01:31:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] i u mjesto juda je blagost,

1843
01:31:47,840 --> 01:31:49,079
[SPEAKER_01] on kaže Buanosera.

1844
01:31:49,079 --> 01:31:51,020
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je tada bilo jasno ko je on.

1845
01:31:51,020 --> 01:31:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, i to je tako.

1846
01:31:52,800 --> 01:31:56,020
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su se nažalost opredijelili,

1847
01:31:56,020 --> 01:31:58,479
[SPEAKER_01] opredijelili se za materijalno,

1848
01:31:58,479 --> 01:31:59,340
[SPEAKER_01] a ne za duhovno.

1849
01:31:59,340 --> 01:32:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo na crkvu.

1850
01:32:00,420 --> 01:32:04,020
[SPEAKER_01] Pa čini je materijalno, zna se što piše tamo u Bibliji,

1851
01:32:04,020 --> 01:32:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] kome služiš.

1852
01:32:05,600 --> 01:32:09,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ili, Bogu Mamonu ili Bogu novca.

1853
01:32:09,640 --> 01:32:12,520
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno, Mamon se simbolizira kao novac,

1854
01:32:12,520 --> 01:32:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] ali u biti je to u prijevodu točnome,

1855
01:32:14,760 --> 01:32:17,359
[SPEAKER_01] znači krivo stečeno bogatstvo.

1856
01:32:17,359 --> 01:32:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je ono, pravi prijevod bi bio,

1857
01:32:20,539 --> 01:32:21,600
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi puninu riječi.

1858
01:32:22,220 --> 01:32:24,539
[SPEAKER_01] Malmona, preveli se.

1859
01:32:24,539 --> 01:32:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] Prima tome danas oni služe,

1860
01:32:26,260 --> 01:32:27,479
[SPEAKER_01] oni se moraju vrati.

1861
01:32:27,479 --> 01:32:30,560
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, prvo crkva mora se vrati.

1862
01:32:30,560 --> 01:32:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] I još ti nešto reći.

1863
01:32:31,579 --> 01:32:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] Nisem nija znao.

1864
01:32:33,079 --> 01:32:35,180
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, uvijek čovjek porad sjegli,

1865
01:32:35,180 --> 01:32:36,100
[SPEAKER_01] život učiti.

1866
01:32:36,100 --> 01:32:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] I ovi su izmislili da se crkva u se kristije,

1867
01:32:40,079 --> 01:32:41,939
[SPEAKER_01] čini se crkvu stavio u se kristije.

1868
01:32:42,420 --> 01:32:43,979
[SPEAKER_01] Od francuske revolucije,

1869
01:32:43,979 --> 01:32:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] zašto je propada Evropa krišćanska?

1870
01:32:46,420 --> 01:32:49,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je dosegla vrkunac o svemu toga smo rekli.

1871
01:32:49,880 --> 01:32:54,020
[SPEAKER_01] Zato jer su prvo iz kulture izbacili vjeru,

1872
01:32:54,020 --> 01:32:57,760
[SPEAKER_01] pa su iz politike izbacili vjeru,

1873
01:32:57,760 --> 01:33:00,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa zato je ta crkve nema.

1874
01:33:00,159 --> 01:33:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ti izbaciš iz znanosti,

1875
01:33:01,760 --> 01:33:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] ti si izbacili vjeru iz te tri stvari.

1876
01:33:03,340 --> 01:33:06,560
[SPEAKER_01] Kad nema znanost, kultura i politika,

1877
01:33:06,560 --> 01:33:09,479
[SPEAKER_01] duhovnog, ona je može biti svašta.

1878
01:33:09,479 --> 01:33:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I svačija.

1879
01:33:10,000 --> 01:33:10,859
[SPEAKER_01] Što si dogodili.

1880
01:33:10,859 --> 01:33:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, bacaje.

1881
01:33:11,539 --> 01:33:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1882
01:33:12,420 --> 01:33:14,460
[SPEAKER_01] I sad se to treba vratiti.

1883
01:33:14,460 --> 01:33:20,140
[SPEAKER_01] I stoji po kanonima katoličke crkve

1884
01:33:20,140 --> 01:33:22,520
[SPEAKER_01] da crkve ni prelati,

1885
01:33:22,520 --> 01:33:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] ili veliko dostajanstvenici,

1886
01:33:23,920 --> 01:33:24,779
[SPEAKER_01] neke države,

1887
01:33:24,779 --> 01:33:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] neći manjati ni čije.

1888
01:33:26,460 --> 01:33:30,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je ta država ugroženi ljezni interes,

1889
01:33:30,659 --> 01:33:32,079
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno narod te države,

1890
01:33:32,079 --> 01:33:34,279
[SPEAKER_01] vjerski i katolički,

1891
01:33:34,279 --> 01:33:38,020
[SPEAKER_01] tada crkva može čak i osnivati stranke

1892
01:33:38,020 --> 01:33:41,020
[SPEAKER_01] i moriti se za vlast da vrati na pravi narod.

1893
01:33:41,539 --> 01:33:45,619
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, prema tome, crkva ovakva koja je pristala

1894
01:33:45,619 --> 01:33:49,260
[SPEAKER_01] da nju financira iz budžeta,

1895
01:33:49,260 --> 01:33:52,180
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatskoga ne je samostalna crkva.

1896
01:33:52,180 --> 01:33:55,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tebi je svaka mlada koja god dođe,

1897
01:33:55,800 --> 01:33:57,880
[SPEAKER_01] a svaka mila gora od prekode njim je dobra.

1898
01:33:57,979 --> 01:33:59,699
[SPEAKER_01] jer da je novac.

1899
01:33:59,699 --> 01:34:00,739
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

1900
01:34:00,739 --> 01:34:01,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ste vi crkva naroda,

1901
01:34:01,939 --> 01:34:03,260
[SPEAKER_01] krisova crkva u narod,

1902
01:34:03,260 --> 01:34:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] narod će vas prepoznati.

1903
01:34:05,260 --> 01:34:07,739
[SPEAKER_01] Narod je hrvatski velikodušan

1904
01:34:07,739 --> 01:34:09,520
[SPEAKER_01] i uvijek je bio sa crkom.

1905
01:34:09,520 --> 01:34:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] S tim više smo mi marijanski narod.

1906
01:34:12,460 --> 01:34:14,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, marijanski narod,

1907
01:34:14,699 --> 01:34:15,819
[SPEAKER_01] mi pripadamo tome.

1908
01:34:15,819 --> 01:34:18,260
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo narod kojeg je svetac,

1909
01:34:18,260 --> 01:34:21,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ivan Pavao II. nazvao narodom Nade.

1910
01:34:21,640 --> 01:34:23,680
[SPEAKER_01] To nije nazvao ni svoj poljski narod.

1911
01:34:23,680 --> 01:34:25,159
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo ti.

1912
01:34:25,159 --> 01:34:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] E pa onda budemo narod Nade.

1913
01:34:27,699 --> 01:34:29,680
[SPEAKER_01] A ne narod bez nađa.

1914
01:34:29,680 --> 01:34:31,199
[SPEAKER_01] Narod bez vjere.

1915
01:34:31,199 --> 01:34:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kako mi mislimo da smo mi bez vjere katolička obstati?

1916
01:34:33,539 --> 01:34:35,319
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako su našli ostali toliko godina?

1917
01:34:35,319 --> 01:34:37,100
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo hrvatski

1918
01:34:37,100 --> 01:34:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatski njim primili u prvo stoljeću.

1919
01:34:38,920 --> 01:34:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] U ovim našim ilirskim,

1920
01:34:41,380 --> 01:34:42,680
[SPEAKER_01] današnjim hrvatskim zemljama

1921
01:34:42,680 --> 01:34:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] na koje je hodio?

1922
01:34:43,579 --> 01:34:44,739
[SPEAKER_01] Sveti Pavel.

1923
01:34:44,739 --> 01:34:48,180
[SPEAKER_01] On piše, ima u poslanici njegov i nima.

1924
01:34:48,180 --> 01:34:50,239
[SPEAKER_01] Sveti Luka,

1925
01:34:50,239 --> 01:34:51,439
[SPEAKER_01] drugi evanđelist,

1926
01:34:51,560 --> 01:34:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] piše u dijelima apostolskim

1927
01:34:54,079 --> 01:34:56,479
[SPEAKER_01] da je on poslao svoje najbolje učenike

1928
01:34:56,479 --> 01:34:58,600
[SPEAKER_01] u zemlju Dalmaciju.

1929
01:34:58,600 --> 01:34:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jako ste inspirirani.

1930
01:34:59,960 --> 01:35:00,680
[SPEAKER_00] Sviđa mi se to.

1931
01:35:00,680 --> 01:35:02,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja još moram par pitanja.

1932
01:35:02,180 --> 01:35:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] U, pa to je puno vezi.

1933
01:35:03,239 --> 01:35:05,060
[SPEAKER_00] Nema veze, brzo ćemo mi to.

1934
01:35:05,060 --> 01:35:08,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ako Ukrajini prijeti primjerice,

1935
01:35:08,399 --> 01:35:09,720
[SPEAKER_00] evo, to su neka blic pitanja,

1936
01:35:09,720 --> 01:35:11,479
[SPEAKER_00] čerupanje, da tako kažem.

1937
01:35:11,479 --> 01:35:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] Prijeti li to čerupanje

1938
01:35:14,960 --> 01:35:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] danas, sutra, možda i na Balkanu?

1939
01:35:17,279 --> 01:35:18,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako.

1940
01:35:18,560 --> 01:35:21,479
[SPEAKER_01] Procesi geopolitički sigurno

1941
01:35:21,479 --> 01:35:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] onim neće više status kvokave,

1942
01:35:23,180 --> 01:35:24,439
[SPEAKER_01] bilo ovo više biti neće.

1943
01:35:24,439 --> 01:35:25,239
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon Ukrajinskog,

1944
01:35:25,239 --> 01:35:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] posredničkog rata,

1945
01:35:26,079 --> 01:35:27,220
[SPEAKER_01] ili kako Rusi zovu

1946
01:35:27,220 --> 01:35:28,100
[SPEAKER_01] specialne operacije,

1947
01:35:28,100 --> 01:35:29,020
[SPEAKER_01] više ništa besi,

1948
01:35:29,020 --> 01:35:30,359
[SPEAKER_01] neće isto pa i tako dalje.

1949
01:35:30,359 --> 01:35:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ta jugoistok Evrope,

1950
01:35:32,260 --> 01:35:34,939
[SPEAKER_01] u knjigu se nema Balkana.

1951
01:35:34,939 --> 01:35:39,220
[SPEAKER_01] Balkan je turska riječ za planinu.

1952
01:35:39,220 --> 01:35:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] Bugari su pobjegli od te riječi

1953
01:35:43,539 --> 01:35:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] i nešto što se može nazvati

1954
01:35:45,239 --> 01:35:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] Balkan je stara planina,

1955
01:35:47,340 --> 01:35:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] a mi smo ostalo,

1956
01:35:48,619 --> 01:35:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] gdje narijedi su alpsko nabiranje.

1957
01:35:50,420 --> 01:35:51,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je stariji.

1958
01:35:51,039 --> 01:35:52,840
[SPEAKER_01] Oni zovu stara planina.

1959
01:35:53,579 --> 01:35:54,979
[SPEAKER_01] Balkan nije polotok.

1960
01:35:54,979 --> 01:35:56,760
[SPEAKER_01] Da je polotok,

1961
01:35:56,760 --> 01:35:58,600
[SPEAKER_01] onda bi ova hopnena,

1962
01:35:58,600 --> 01:36:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer definicija polotoka

1963
01:36:00,000 --> 01:36:01,399
[SPEAKER_01] bila kraća,

1964
01:36:01,399 --> 01:36:03,600
[SPEAKER_01] a nije ovdje duža

1965
01:36:03,600 --> 01:36:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] od ove ostale dvije.

1966
01:36:04,800 --> 01:36:05,600
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedno.

1967
01:36:05,600 --> 01:36:06,420
[SPEAKER_01] Polotok je,

1968
01:36:06,420 --> 01:36:08,020
[SPEAKER_01] mora kroz cijeli njega

1969
01:36:08,020 --> 01:36:09,699
[SPEAKER_01] imati maritimne utjecaje.

1970
01:36:09,699 --> 01:36:12,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo ne ima maritimnih utjecaja,

1971
01:36:12,140 --> 01:36:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] šta ima u sredini,

1972
01:36:13,239 --> 01:36:14,520
[SPEAKER_01] tamo oko Drine,

1973
01:36:14,520 --> 01:36:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] Bosne i Hercegovine,

1974
01:36:15,840 --> 01:36:17,479
[SPEAKER_01] nekakvi maritimnih utjecaja,

1975
01:36:17,479 --> 01:36:17,819
[SPEAKER_01] nije ima.

1976
01:36:17,920 --> 01:36:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa preto ne možemo i polotok,

1977
01:36:19,300 --> 01:36:21,279
[SPEAKER_01] pa ni ćemo po zemljopis

1978
01:36:21,279 --> 01:36:22,180
[SPEAKER_01] koji se zove znanost.

1979
01:36:22,180 --> 01:36:25,640
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se zove inače

1980
01:36:25,640 --> 01:36:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji se zove Italija?

1981
01:36:28,239 --> 01:36:29,979
[SPEAKER_00] Apeninski polotok.

1982
01:36:29,979 --> 01:36:30,680
[SPEAKER_01] Aha, po čemu?

1983
01:36:30,680 --> 01:36:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] Po Apeninima.

1984
01:36:31,880 --> 01:36:33,020
[SPEAKER_01] Dobre, Pirinejski.

1985
01:36:33,020 --> 01:36:34,359
[SPEAKER_00] Isto po Pirinejima.

1986
01:36:34,359 --> 01:36:35,399
[SPEAKER_01] Isto i Skandinavski.

1987
01:36:35,399 --> 01:36:37,399
[SPEAKER_01] Pa na tome da je polotok,

1988
01:36:37,399 --> 01:36:37,840
[SPEAKER_01] a nije,

1989
01:36:37,840 --> 01:36:40,060
[SPEAKER_01] onda se ovo ne može zovati Balkan,

1990
01:36:40,060 --> 01:36:41,420
[SPEAKER_01] nego bi se,

1991
01:36:41,420 --> 01:36:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] kako je zvao,

1992
01:36:42,039 --> 01:36:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] Dinarik.

1993
01:36:42,659 --> 01:36:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] I ja ga u svojom knjizi

1994
01:36:44,279 --> 01:36:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] zovem Dinarik.

1995
01:36:45,739 --> 01:36:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] Po Dinarik.

1996
01:36:46,920 --> 01:36:48,479
[SPEAKER_01] E, dakle,

1997
01:36:48,479 --> 01:36:50,619
[SPEAKER_01] i to smo raštisili,

1998
01:36:50,619 --> 01:36:51,279
[SPEAKER_01] ova šta ima.

1999
01:36:51,279 --> 01:36:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] Može.

2000
01:36:51,840 --> 01:36:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

2001
01:36:52,819 --> 01:36:55,720
[SPEAKER_01] A glavno izvorište je

2002
01:36:55,720 --> 01:36:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] stvaranje velike Albanije.

2003
01:36:58,000 --> 01:37:00,180
[SPEAKER_01] A veliku Alban,

2004
01:37:00,180 --> 01:37:01,560
[SPEAKER_01] to je američki plan,

2005
01:37:01,560 --> 01:37:02,760
[SPEAKER_01] isključivo američki,

2006
01:37:02,760 --> 01:37:04,220
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, nema Evropa s tim.

2007
01:37:04,220 --> 01:37:05,939
[SPEAKER_01] Zato se gradi sada,

2008
01:37:05,939 --> 01:37:06,699
[SPEAKER_01] pored tiranije,

2009
01:37:06,699 --> 01:37:08,560
[SPEAKER_01] tamo velika baza.

2010
01:37:08,560 --> 01:37:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] A velika baza,

2011
01:37:10,539 --> 01:37:11,420
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je napravljena,

2012
01:37:11,420 --> 01:37:13,760
[SPEAKER_01] 99. godine nakon toga,

2013
01:37:13,760 --> 01:37:14,880
[SPEAKER_01] nakon bombardiranja,

2014
01:37:14,880 --> 01:37:16,560
[SPEAKER_01] je u bolj stilu,

2015
01:37:16,560 --> 01:37:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] u Oroševcu,

2016
01:37:17,260 --> 01:37:18,340
[SPEAKER_01] na Kosovu.

2017
01:37:18,340 --> 01:37:18,979
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Kosovu.

2018
01:37:18,979 --> 01:37:20,159
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto je ona tu napravljena?

2019
01:37:20,159 --> 01:37:22,939
[SPEAKER_01] Zato jer je ona na sredini

2020
01:37:22,939 --> 01:37:24,619
[SPEAKER_01] između Crnog mora i Jadrana.

2021
01:37:24,619 --> 01:37:26,220
[SPEAKER_01] A Jadrana na sredini

2022
01:37:26,220 --> 01:37:27,359
[SPEAKER_01] u sredozemljeg mora

2023
01:37:27,359 --> 01:37:28,479
[SPEAKER_01] da se može kontrolirati.

2024
01:37:28,479 --> 01:37:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Inače,

2025
01:37:28,960 --> 01:37:30,819
[SPEAKER_01] jedna je u geostrategiji

2026
01:37:30,819 --> 01:37:31,479
[SPEAKER_01] zanimljivost,

2027
01:37:31,479 --> 01:37:32,600
[SPEAKER_01] kada se uzme u šestar

2028
01:37:32,600 --> 01:37:33,819
[SPEAKER_01] i opisa se kružnica

2029
01:37:33,819 --> 01:37:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] od Moskve do Teherana,

2030
01:37:36,739 --> 01:37:38,640
[SPEAKER_01] u kilometar je jednaka udaljenost.

2031
01:37:38,640 --> 01:37:40,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa nije,

2032
01:37:40,479 --> 01:37:41,560
[SPEAKER_01] je matematika.

2033
01:37:41,560 --> 01:37:42,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa nije slučajno.

2034
01:37:42,439 --> 01:37:43,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, matematika je čista,

2035
01:37:43,819 --> 01:37:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] luluja je čista matematika,

2036
01:37:46,539 --> 01:37:47,359
[SPEAKER_01] teorija skupova,

2037
01:37:47,359 --> 01:37:48,239
[SPEAKER_01] to je uvjerojatno

2038
01:37:48,239 --> 01:37:49,560
[SPEAKER_01] sad je nevana i teorija igala,

2039
01:37:49,560 --> 01:37:50,899
[SPEAKER_01] ali da je sad ne zamarastim.

2040
01:37:50,899 --> 01:37:52,199
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je.

2041
01:37:52,199 --> 01:37:54,020
[SPEAKER_01] A ta velika Albanija

2042
01:37:54,020 --> 01:37:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] je bila Albanija,

2043
01:37:54,880 --> 01:37:56,180
[SPEAKER_01] bila Kosovo,

2044
01:37:56,180 --> 01:37:58,199
[SPEAKER_01] jedna trećina

2045
01:37:58,199 --> 01:37:59,939
[SPEAKER_01] zapadna Makedonija,

2046
01:38:00,739 --> 01:38:01,859
[SPEAKER_01] ove dvije općine

2047
01:38:01,859 --> 01:38:03,720
[SPEAKER_01] Bujanovac i Preševo u Srbiji,

2048
01:38:03,720 --> 01:38:05,340
[SPEAKER_01] jedan dio Crne Gore,

2049
01:38:05,340 --> 01:38:07,739
[SPEAKER_01] čak jedan manji dio Grške.

2050
01:38:07,739 --> 01:38:09,439
[SPEAKER_01] To bila Albanija,

2051
01:38:09,439 --> 01:38:12,279
[SPEAKER_01] koja bi po njihovim zasadama,

2052
01:38:12,279 --> 01:38:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] američkim,

2053
01:38:13,800 --> 01:38:16,779
[SPEAKER_01] bila dovoljno kompaktna cijelina

2054
01:38:16,779 --> 01:38:17,960
[SPEAKER_01] da jedne strane

2055
01:38:17,960 --> 01:38:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] zaustavi projekciju

2056
01:38:19,579 --> 01:38:20,600
[SPEAKER_01] nakon Ukrajine,

2057
01:38:20,600 --> 01:38:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] projekciju moći Rusije

2058
01:38:22,500 --> 01:38:24,619
[SPEAKER_01] prema sredini sredozemlja,

2059
01:38:24,619 --> 01:38:26,520
[SPEAKER_01] zato smo je Hrvatska bitna.

2060
01:38:26,520 --> 01:38:28,920
[SPEAKER_01] Jer smo jedna od četiri

2061
01:38:28,920 --> 01:38:30,619
[SPEAKER_01] gravitacijske stožerne

2062
01:38:30,619 --> 01:38:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] točke Evrope,

2063
01:38:31,840 --> 01:38:34,819
[SPEAKER_01] a takvih ima samo 17 u svijetu,

2064
01:38:34,819 --> 01:38:35,939
[SPEAKER_01] četiri u Evropi.

2065
01:38:35,939 --> 01:38:37,220
[SPEAKER_01] I za moji gledatelji

2066
01:38:37,220 --> 01:38:37,819
[SPEAKER_01] da znaju,

2067
01:38:37,819 --> 01:38:38,979
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je geostrategija

2068
01:38:38,979 --> 01:38:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] najviše razine.

2069
01:38:39,760 --> 01:38:41,460
[SPEAKER_01] Te četiri točke su

2070
01:38:41,460 --> 01:38:42,600
[SPEAKER_01] La Manche,

2071
01:38:42,600 --> 01:38:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] Gibratar,

2072
01:38:43,960 --> 01:38:45,399
[SPEAKER_01] Bospor,

2073
01:38:45,399 --> 01:38:45,920
[SPEAKER_01] Daneli,

2074
01:38:45,920 --> 01:38:47,560
[SPEAKER_01] Otrant i Jadran.

2075
01:38:47,560 --> 01:38:48,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ko drži

2076
01:38:48,659 --> 01:38:50,600
[SPEAKER_01] dvije trećine Jadrana?

2077
01:38:50,600 --> 01:38:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvati,

2078
01:38:51,119 --> 01:38:52,180
[SPEAKER_01] ne talijan nego mi.

2079
01:38:52,180 --> 01:38:55,439
[SPEAKER_01] Oni jesu na uglazu Otranta,

2080
01:38:55,439 --> 01:38:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] s druge strane Albanija.

2081
01:38:56,579 --> 01:38:57,140
[SPEAKER_01] Albanija, da.

2082
01:38:57,140 --> 01:38:58,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je bitno Jadran,

2083
01:38:58,020 --> 01:38:59,140
[SPEAKER_01] jer kao more

2084
01:38:59,140 --> 01:39:00,439
[SPEAKER_01] koje se najviše ulači

2085
01:39:00,500 --> 01:39:01,640
[SPEAKER_01] u Evropsko kopno.

2086
01:39:01,640 --> 01:39:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] I zato sve od Skandinavije

2087
01:39:04,380 --> 01:39:05,520
[SPEAKER_01] i Središnje Evrope,

2088
01:39:05,520 --> 01:39:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatska je još jedno

2089
01:39:06,760 --> 01:39:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] po geostratečkih zasadama,

2090
01:39:08,220 --> 01:39:08,720
[SPEAKER_01] ovih ne znam,

2091
01:39:08,720 --> 01:39:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] to bi svaki učenik

2092
01:39:09,760 --> 01:39:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] ne može izići

2093
01:39:10,539 --> 01:39:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] iz razreda bilo kojega

2094
01:39:12,079 --> 01:39:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] od osnovne škole

2095
01:39:12,800 --> 01:39:13,979
[SPEAKER_01] da ovo ne zna šta ću reći.

2096
01:39:13,979 --> 01:39:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatska je jedina zemlja

2097
01:39:16,380 --> 01:39:17,039
[SPEAKER_01] u Evropi

2098
01:39:17,039 --> 01:39:18,060
[SPEAKER_01] koja je isto dobno

2099
01:39:18,060 --> 01:39:19,100
[SPEAKER_01] srednjoevropska

2100
01:39:19,100 --> 01:39:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] i srednozemna zemlja.

2101
01:39:21,199 --> 01:39:22,180
[SPEAKER_01] Jedina, nemate druge.

2102
01:39:22,180 --> 01:39:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] To smo učili, da.

2103
01:39:23,159 --> 01:39:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bar nekada.

2104
01:39:24,000 --> 01:39:25,399
[SPEAKER_01] To ti govori vrijedno

2105
01:39:25,399 --> 01:39:26,380
[SPEAKER_01] zašto se svi bore

2106
01:39:26,380 --> 01:39:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] ti sve ne pojel.

2107
01:39:27,720 --> 01:39:28,939
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto je Hrvatska važna

2108
01:39:28,939 --> 01:39:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] pa i za rusku geopolitiku

2109
01:39:30,239 --> 01:39:30,939
[SPEAKER_01] a ne Srbije?

2110
01:39:30,939 --> 01:39:32,159
[SPEAKER_01] Iz ovih razloga što sam sada.

2111
01:39:32,159 --> 01:39:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ja moguće čarupanje Hrvatske?

2112
01:39:33,720 --> 01:39:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] Malo prije ste rekli...

2113
01:39:34,960 --> 01:39:36,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, čarupanje.

2114
01:39:36,020 --> 01:39:37,359
[SPEAKER_01] Šta više se može očarupati

2115
01:39:37,359 --> 01:39:37,939
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatske?

2116
01:39:37,939 --> 01:39:39,119
[SPEAKER_01] Više nema šta očarupati.

2117
01:39:39,119 --> 01:39:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao se ono što ima.

2118
01:39:40,079 --> 01:39:41,920
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo jedino razgovarati

2119
01:39:41,920 --> 01:39:42,560
[SPEAKER_01] da mi govorimo

2120
01:39:42,560 --> 01:39:44,520
[SPEAKER_01] o objedinjenju Hrvatske zemlja.

2121
01:39:44,520 --> 01:39:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] O tome da?

2122
01:39:45,039 --> 01:39:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] Aha, znači imamo

2123
01:39:45,819 --> 01:39:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] veće pove dobro.

2124
01:39:45,920 --> 01:39:47,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, čarupanje, više nema.

2125
01:39:47,500 --> 01:39:48,899
[SPEAKER_01] Nemaš više šta očarupati?

2126
01:39:48,899 --> 01:39:49,899
[SPEAKER_00] Malo prije ste rekli

2127
01:39:49,899 --> 01:39:50,779
[SPEAKER_00] kako je 30%...

2128
01:39:50,779 --> 01:39:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] Šta očarupati kada resimo

2129
01:39:51,880 --> 01:39:53,079
[SPEAKER_01] doli kod Ljute

2130
01:39:53,079 --> 01:39:54,560
[SPEAKER_01] iza Dubrovnika u Konovala?

2131
01:39:54,680 --> 01:39:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znate koliko je udalje od zračne lidije?

2132
01:39:56,079 --> 01:39:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] 800 metara.

2133
01:39:56,880 --> 01:39:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] Eto ga.

2134
01:39:57,859 --> 01:40:00,319
[SPEAKER_00] Rekli ste da je 30%...

2135
01:40:00,319 --> 01:40:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] E, ajde, oprostite.

2136
01:40:00,960 --> 01:40:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] E, završio.

2137
01:40:01,500 --> 01:40:02,979
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je Velika Albanija

2138
01:40:02,979 --> 01:40:04,899
[SPEAKER_01] koja će imati jednu zadat

2139
01:40:04,899 --> 01:40:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] da uzme projekciju

2140
01:40:05,739 --> 01:40:06,859
[SPEAKER_01] moći Rusije nakonoga.

2141
01:40:06,859 --> 01:40:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] A druga,

2142
01:40:08,039 --> 01:40:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] isto je to,

2143
01:40:09,460 --> 01:40:10,199
[SPEAKER_01] isti dio isto,

2144
01:40:10,199 --> 01:40:11,100
[SPEAKER_01] to su strategije,

2145
01:40:11,100 --> 01:40:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] da prekine kineski put Svile

2146
01:40:13,699 --> 01:40:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] koja ide od Kine,

2147
01:40:15,539 --> 01:40:16,800
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj, kako se zove,

2148
01:40:16,800 --> 01:40:18,899
[SPEAKER_01] Irana i sve ostaloga,

2149
01:40:18,899 --> 01:40:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] gdje završava kineski put Svile?

2150
01:40:20,880 --> 01:40:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] U Rijecu,

2151
01:40:22,420 --> 01:40:23,260
[SPEAKER_01] sa Vudrijskoj Vali.

2152
01:40:24,180 --> 01:40:24,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to vidiš,

2153
01:40:24,739 --> 01:40:26,479
[SPEAKER_01] i po tome je Hrvatska i ostalo.

2154
01:40:26,479 --> 01:40:27,359
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nije slučajno

2155
01:40:27,359 --> 01:40:28,600
[SPEAKER_01] kineski radilo

2156
01:40:28,600 --> 01:40:29,579
[SPEAKER_01] najmovez na pelješcu.

2157
01:40:29,579 --> 01:40:30,899
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, da smo mi zapravo

